 
<p>
With Rubio's <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/07/07/rubios-cruel-paid-leave-plan-forces-families-pay-back-benefits-after-parents">plan for parental leave loans against Social Security</a>,
*"when mom or dad tragically dies a few years after having their
third kid, the surviving spouse will have to send a big fat check to
the SSA,"* until it is all paid back.

 